      "message": "feat: Mental Models Framework - Cognitive Tools from Chinese Metaphysics\n\n## New Module: lib/mental_models/\nComprehensive mental models framework derived from Five Element philosophy:\n\n### Core Files\n- frameworks.ts: 15 mental models from Five Elements\n  - 3 models per element (Wood, Fire, Earth, Metal, Water)\n  - Each with application, triggers, antidotes, classical origins\n- utils.ts: Helper functions for working with models\n- index.ts: Module exports\n- README.md: Complete documentation\n\n### Decision Frameworks (5)\n1. Five Element Decision Matrix (五行决) - Multi-factor decisions\n2. Seasonal Timing Framework (待时而动) - When to act\n3. Ten God Interaction Model (十神应用) - Relationship analysis\n4. Branch Interaction Strategy (地支运筹) - Hidden dynamics\n5. Root and Branch Analysis (本末先后) - Finding leverage points\n\n### Cognitive Bias Detection (6)\n- Excessive Wood/Fire/Earth/Metal/Water biases\n- Missing Element Blindness\n\n### API Integration\n- /api/mental-models - REST API for model access\n- Search, filter by element, get recommendations\n\n### Report Integration\n- Mental model cards in interpretation report\n- Daily strategy cards\n- Bias warning cards\n- Core mental model highlight\n\nVeritas Vult",
